casebody.data:
No. 08-1332. City of Ontario, California, et al., Petitioners v. Jeff Quon, et al. 559 U.S. 1047, 130 S. Ct. 2366, 2010 U.S. LEXIS 2956.

176 L. Ed. 2d 560,

April 5, 2010.

Motion of the Solicitor General for leave to participate in oral argument as amicus curiae and for divided argument granted. Motion of The Rutherford Institute for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted.
